### 用户认证
### ============================================

### 用户注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 用户登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 用户登录（测试用户）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 用户登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 刷新Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

